[br]use fear to hold agro, great idea, i haven't heard that one before.

i usually doom, ignite, splurt, send pet (taunt off), coc, ebolt and then vex.  run a bit, sit (for extra agro and med).  recast doom until dead, running and sitting for the agro+med.  i see some necros run in circles around the mob, but where i have space, i'd rather run a ways and sit (too many years playing a druid). i always have doom timed so i know when to re-apply. i usually start around the 1:15 mark, in case of resists.

with this routine, i never have to stop (except to re-buff). i run this cycle of spells on yard trash in PoN. i can't wait until 58, pyro should make it much easier. then 60, FP should help a ton. the 59 pet should help some, but it's harder to quantify.
